                                                      " Ristorante Mare Nostro: The Charm of the Mediterranean On the seaside, an Italian dream that warms your heart... Ristorante Mare Nostro merges the freshest flavors of the Mediterranean with a sophisticated atmosphere. Whether it’s for a romantic dinner or a special celebration, Mare Nostro welcomes you and your guests with warm hospitality. From seafood to traditional Italian desserts, its extensive menu  appeals to every palate, making this restaurant a must-visit stop on your journey.",
                                                      "Special & Mr Martini: An Unforgettable Experience  Special & Mr Martini stands out with its unique decoration and warm atmosphere, offering a meticulously designed space. Each room has its own story and aesthetic, providing guests with a distinctive lodging experience. With delicious cuisine and quality service, it promises memorable moments. An ideal choice to make your journey special!",
